WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:03.797
Welcome to the Inspections tutorial.

00:03.797 --> 00:06.857
Step 1: Create an Inspection.

00:06.857 --> 00:11.498
Enter job details, location, and claim type.

00:11.498 --> 00:14.135
Step 2: Capture Evidence.

00:14.135 --> 00:22.135
Upload photos, add annotations, and record moisture readings directly in the app.

00:22.135 --> 00:24.135
Step 3: Sign Off.

00:24.135 --> 00:32.135
Both the client and technician provide digital signatures with automatic timestamps.

00:32.135 --> 00:34.135
Step 4: Submit.

00:34.135 --> 00:42.135
The inspection auto-generates a report, exports to PDF, and publishes to the client portal.

00:42.135 --> 00:47.620
Your evidence chain is now complete and audit-ready.